      <p>
        Silica rewards nodes for contributing to real-world computing projects while securing the network:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Tasks:</strong> BOINC/Folding@Home jobs, AI model training, scientific workloads.</li>
        <li><strong>Execution:</strong> Nodes perform useful work and produce cryptographic digests.</li>
        <li><strong>Proofs:</strong> Results are compressed into Merkle receipts, batched, and anchored in lineations (periodic chain anchors).</li>
      </ul>

